{"id": "1323930450640764939", "channel_id": "1323627848501694535", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "目前來看應該是沒新內容沒錯，但是新增了超維血肉 超維深海 深海血肉三種玩法，我是覺得說除非這三個界域有特別強勢再來思考是否要加強混沌的共生 or 砍這三種玩法", "timestamp": "2025-01-01T08:26:56.871000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1323627848501694535", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：V2.0 双界域混编", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
